Que 17)What are Root, Parent, Child & Nested elements?
------------------------------------------------------
Root element → The main element of an HTML document. In HTML, the <html> tag is the root element.
Parent element → An element that contains other elements inside it.
Child element → An element that is inside another element.
Nested element → When elements are placed inside other elements.
Example:
<html>
<body>
<p>Hello</p>
</body>
</html>
<html> → Root
<body> → Child of <html> and parent of <p>
<p> → Child element
<p> inside <body> → Nested element
