Que 27) What are the 5 Types of Links in HTML?
-------------------------------------------------
1️⃣ External Link – Links to another website.
<a href="https://www.google.com">Google</a>
2️⃣ Internal Link – Links to another page within the same website.
<a href="about.html">About Us</a>
3️⃣ Anchor (Bookmark) Link – Links to a specific section of the same page.
<a href="#contact">Go to Contact</a>
4️⃣ Email Link – Opens the email application to send an email.
<a href="mailto:example@gmail.com">Send Email</a>
5️⃣ Image Link – An image used as a clickable link.
<a href="home.html"><img src="logo.png"></a>
